# BDA Project â€” Image Caption Generator


FastAPI backend + React frontend to generate captions for images using a Hugging Face model.


## Run (backend)
cd backend
python -m venv venv
# PowerShell:
.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn backend:app --reload --port 8000


## Run (frontend)
cd frontend/caption-ui
npm install
npm start


## Notes
- The first time you call the /caption endpoint the backend downloads the model (~1GB) and may take time.
- Do not commit large model files; use .gitignore.
